  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dca\u0da9\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db1\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2\u2019\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Ranil is not a fool\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Sajith Premadasa, the opposition leader, questioned how Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, who went home after being defeated in Colombo, could become a leader.",
        "The opposition leader said that some people say that Ranil Wickremesinghe is a crook and went home after losing from the Colombo district.",
        "However, Mr. Premadasa said that he does not question the method by which Ranil Wickremesinghe became the President and that the appointment was done constitutionally.",
        "He further said that if he had promised to protect Rajapaksa's band of thieves, he would be the president of the country today."
      ],
